=item B<_story_for_rss>

 _story_for_rss topic story_id

Generates a story link in RSS format.
=cut
<item>
	<title>{-story_title|$0|$1}</title>
	<link>{-aurl|STORY|topic|$0|id|$1}</link>
	<author>{-user_email|{-story_userid|$0|$1}} ({-user_username|{-story_userid|$0|$1}})</author>
	<description>
<![CDATA[
{-story_abstract|$0|$1}
]]>
	</description>
</item>
